@startuml
!theme plain
title Data Flow in Movalytics Data Warehouse

participant "Kaggle API" as Kaggle
participant "FRED API" as FRED
participant "S3 Bucket" as S3
participant "Apache Airflow" as Airflow
participant "Apache Spark" as Spark
participant "Amazon Redshift" as Redshift

Airflow -> Kaggle : Extract MovieLens dataset
Kaggle --> Airflow : Return movie data
Airflow -> FRED : Extract CPI dataset
FRED --> Airflow : Return CPI data
Airflow -> S3 : Store raw data
Airflow -> Spark : Trigger data transformation
Spark -> S3 : Read raw data
S3 --> Spark : Return raw data
Spark -> Spark : Transform data
Spark -> Redshift : Load data to staging tables
Airflow -> Redshift : Execute SQL for dimension tables
Airflow -> Redshift : Perform data quality checks
Redshift --> Airflow : Return check results
@enduml